Package: ggchromatic
Title: Colourspace Scales for ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Teun",
           family = "van den Brand",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tahvdbrand@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9335-7468"))
Description: The 'ggchromatic' package provides additional colour and fill 
  scales to use with 'ggplot2'. It uses the 'ggplot2' extension system to map 
  a number of variables to different colourspaces with the 'farver' package.
